        "text": ". It continued seven years, just as long again as that in the time of Elijah. For if a wicked nation will not be reformed by a lesser judgment, they must expect to be visited with a greater. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The sons of the prophets were sitting before him — ",
        "children": []
